{"tid":589082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日研發新藥 只用1粒 一天內殺死流感病毒 預計最快要在2019年能獲得批准在美國上市","createTime":"2018-03-11T15:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-31T07:01:54.000Z","uid":3393,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"323a78f4a6f954b0b7f3045a765faee8bb58d97f","tid":589082,"uid":3393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T15:59:26.000Z","msg":"就在十年以來最嚴重的流感病毒肆虐全球的同時，日本Shionogi 製藥公司研發出一種可在一天之內殺死流感病毒的新藥。這款藥上月獲得了日本藥監局的加速批准上市。<br />\n<br />\n和目前市面上普遍使用的流感藥物 &mdash;&mdash;羅氏製藥的達菲&mdash;&mdash;需要三天時間才能殺死流感病毒相比，這款叫做Xofluza的新藥通過抑制一種流感病毒複製必需的酶，可在24小時內快速從體內清除大部份病毒。儘管Xofluza需要和達菲差不多的時間才能使病人完全恢復，但是對於服用Xofluza的病人來說，由於病毒的快速清除，身體的流感症狀也可能更輕，且消退更快。<br />\n<br />\n此外，這款新藥整個療程只需服用一粒。而達菲則需連續服用五天，每天兩次。如果病人忘記服藥，還可能導致病毒捲土重來，使感染時間加強。<br />\n<br />\n今年的流感病毒來勢洶洶。根據美國疾病控制中心的數據，今年流感疫苗的有效率僅為36%。而對於今年最主要的流感病毒H3N2來說，疫苗的防禦效果只有25%。<br />\n<br />\n由於流感病毒的不斷變種，也給疫苗製造商預測下一年流感病毒的基因序列不斷加大難度。很多製造商開始致力於開發覆蓋面更廣、可持續好幾個季度的通用疫苗。但是要等到新的疫苗投放市場可能還要幾年的時間。<br />\n<br />\n據《華爾街日報》報導，目前Shionogi 公司計劃於今年向美國食品藥品監督管理局（FDA）提交這款新藥的申請，預計最快要在2019年能獲得批准在美國上市。◇<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/18/3/6/n10194484.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.epochtimes.com%2Fb5%2F18%2F3%2F6%2Fn10194484.htm&d=Mc4KseLfJtuR7deRXvtNeU%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=7241f82b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/18/3/6/n10194484.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ccb3dbe4001b0d5595ba013b85154da4a9a26215","tid":589082,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:03:24.000Z","msg":"大幅降低打工仔射波日數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73ffc33ca6a4ac13a02d0951c6192214326cba67","tid":589082,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:03:54.000Z","msg":"You know too much <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d940e3e4e8f4cc4a96b5fbeb78e60e79e58b734","tid":589082,"uid":4326,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:16:24.000Z","msg":"殺死埋個病人"},{"pid":"ae65cbe10bb2bdc63dcfc9c3d0932c9b4ab7340e","tid":589082,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:17:30.000Z","msg":"等睇白老鼠"},{"pid":"6d0fd54b219c74e2880be3a82bcc1d5165007524","tid":589082,"uid":34103,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:18:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f57e90f51f5132f4da83447839ba35d620d57d7e","tid":589082,"uid":52946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:20:20.000Z","msg":"幾時會發生生化危機"},{"pid":"f4aeaf7ee669fe4b920d427c7e86e511e0a45d6d","tid":589082,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:24:18.000Z","msg":"即係抗生素?"},{"pid":"0e46ca27cc724cb89f587c599d84384faf5a30b9","tid":589082,"uid":55568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:44:15.000Z","msg":"日本班社畜為左返工真係咩都做得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70bbf773389cceba0c2764763b7c4d13bedb392c","tid":589082,"uid":172497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:55:20.000Z","msg":"大日本帝國既製藥技術真係好強勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e47f1a389fdae51ec781d1a42068dda3ada89c3","tid":589082,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:58:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a9694c49c685e4c26c2221f2f7be38445847aa5e","tid":589082,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e47f1a389fdae51ec781d1a42068dda3ada89c3","tid":589082,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"70bbf773389cceba0c2764763b7c4d13bedb392c","tid":589082,"uid":172497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T16:55:20.000Z","